# Test Plan Index

This project has 36 area-specific test plans in `test/plans/`. Each plan documents the features for that area and provides a hybrid checklist of automated (`[A]`) and manual (`[M]`) test items.

## Checklist Notation

- `[A]` -- Fully automatable via Playwright or REST API tests
- `[M]` -- Requires human interaction (drag-drop, voice input, visual verification)
- `[P]` -- Partially automated (Cursor runs the test, human verifies the result)

